{"tid":2449733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"敵華人數倍增》45%美國民眾認為：中國就是最大敵人　倍增至歷史新高","createTime":"2021-03-17T02:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T12:00:04.000Z","uid":35519,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3e30ff55d2f5c7464629d3d826b99b8da394afe7","tid":2449733,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">敵華人數倍增》<br />\n45%美國民眾認為：中國就是最大敵人<br />\n倍增至歷史新高</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://content.gallup.com/origin/gallupinc/GallupSpaces/Production/Cms/POLL/jz_qqmtgwkcymqr-hq4mpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.gallup.com%2Forigin%2Fgallupinc%2FGallupSpaces%2FProduction%2FCms%2FPOLL%2Fjz_qqmtgwkcymqr-hq4mpq.jpg&h=25094caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n◉ 蓋洛普(Gallup)3月16日公佈的調查顯示，美國人視中國為最大敵人(enemy)的比例創新高。<br />\n◉ 超過一半的美國人認為中國是領導全球經濟的大國。<br />\n◉ 創紀錄的63％的美國人認為，中國的經濟力量是對美國屬嚴重威脅(critical threat)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7r7SEMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7r7SEMr.png&h=0446418a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n民調顯示，相較去年美國人對中國的敵視程度，於眾多國家中唯一錄得雙位數百分點增幅。被侵侵以無人機炮製成將軍肉醬意粉的伊朗，美國人對其的敵視程度更罕見下降15個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n蓋洛普上月的民意調查亦發現，美國人對中國的好感度連年下降，使該數字降至歷史最低水平的20％。<br />\n<br />\n人們對俄羅斯是美國最大敵人的看法目前為26％，與一年前23％的人所認為的相比，基本持平，而且與2019年整體排名第一的32％相比有所下降。2018年，有51％的人將朝鮮列為最大敵人。時至今日，僅9％的人仍認為朝鮮是朝鮮最大的敵人，這是值得關注的轉折。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://content.gallup.com/origin/gallupinc/GallupSpaces/Production/Cms/POLL/d_3ejlzu-0k76xxjoctf_a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.gallup.com%2Forigin%2Fgallupinc%2FGallupSpaces%2FProduction%2FCms%2FPOLL%2Fd_3ejlzu-0k76xxjoctf_a.png&h=01533684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在美國最大敵人的看法上，存在明顯的黨派分歧：<br />\n共和黨人將中國列為最大敵國，而民主黨人則認為是俄羅斯為主。76％的共和黨人將中國列為最大敵人，而43％的中立人士和22％的民主黨人持這種看法。<br />\n相反，將近一半的民主黨人認為俄羅斯(47％)才是最大敵人，相比之下，僅四分之一的中立人士(24％)和6％共和黨人所見相同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qParrr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qParrr.png&h=6a44a231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://content.gallup.com/origin/gallupinc/GallupSpaces/Production/Cms/POLL/g7cp_xc-8eop8cfwv1l-bw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.gallup.com%2Forigin%2Fgallupinc%2FGallupSpaces%2FProduction%2FCms%2FPOLL%2Fg7cp_xc-8eop8cfwv1l-bw.png&h=7236b966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未有中文新聞講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上文內容自行簡單翻譯<br />\n<br />\nNew High in Perceptions of China as U.S.'s Greatest Enemy<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gallup.com/poll/337457/new-high-perceptions-china-greatest-enemy.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F337457%2Fnew-high-perceptions-china-greatest-enemy.aspx&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=fdc8fe56\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gallup.com/poll/337457/new-high-perceptions-china-greatest-enemy.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n完整民意調查報告(PDF)<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gallup.com/file/poll/337694/210312China.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Ffile%2Fpoll%2F337694%2F210312China.pdf&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=f19c11bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gallup.com/file/poll/337694/210312China.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"7b738197e14eb7d2efcbcccfbd4bd6cee6001f84","tid":2449733,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"到今時今日都係得45%，唔過半數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7290ff64050d84deb6f83fe9784626733fbf67e1","tid":2449733,"uid":19557,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"睇黎侵侵好快可以出返黎 廢登場戲好快謝幕"},{"pid":"dce72b31b48ffcee0d416fbc36ab9cec31a56b61","tid":2449733,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b738197e14eb7d2efcbcccfbd4bd6cee6001f84